{{Infobox Union |name= KVPU |country= [[Ukraine]] |affiliation= [[International Trade Union Confederation|ITUC]] |members= |full_name= Confederation of Free Trade Unions of Ukraine |native_name= Конфедерація вільних профспілок України |image= |founded= |current= |head= |dissolved_date= |dissolved_state= |merged_into= |office= [[Kiev]], Ukraine |people= |website= [http://www.kvpu.org.ua www.kvpu.org.ua] |footnotes= }} <!-- Include all unused fields for future use. See [[template talk:Infobox Union]] for usage. -->
The '''Confederation of Free Trade Unions of Ukraine''' (KVPU) ({{lang-uk|Конфедерація вільних профспілок України}}) is a [[national trade union center]] in [[Ukraine]]. It is affiliated with the [[International Trade Union Confederation]].
It is one of the few trade unions in Ukraine recognized by the [[AFL-CIO]] as "being independent and honest in its representation of the interests of labor".<ref>[http://www.kyivpost.com/news/nation/detail/91313/ A new generation emerges on national stage], [[Kyiv Post]] (November 25, 2010)</ref>
