{{Infobox rugby league football competition | name = Malta Rugby Union National Championship | current_season = 2016–17 Cisk Lager League | logo = | pixels = | alt = | sport = [[Rugby union]] | formerly = | founded = | inaugural = | folded = | replaced = | ceotag = | ceo = | teams = 4 | countrytag = | country = [[Malta]] | gov_body = | championtag = | champion = | season = | most_champs = | count = | website = | TV = | qualification = | related_comps = [[Malta Rugby Union National Cup|Mediterranean Bank Cup]] and [[Ray Elliot Cup]] }} The ''Malta Rugby Union National Championship'', better known as the '''Cisk Lager League'''<ref>http://www.timesofmalta.com/articles/view/20081219/sport/rugby-cisk-lager-league.237858</ref><ref>http://www.independent.com.mt/articles/2007-03-17/sports-others/Rugby-Cisk-Lager-Championship:-Stompers-clash-with-Kavallieri-170644</ref><ref>http://www.maltatoday.com.mt/sports/rugby/34267/majestic-kavallieri-cruise-to-cisk-lager-league-championship#.WJ9S2jsrJPY</ref><ref>http://www.farsons.com/en/news-detail/20060411-cisk-lager-major-sponsor-of-malta-rugby-football-union</ref><ref>http://www.airmalta.com/destinations/malta/best-of-malta/sports/rugby</ref><ref>http://www.sportinmalta.com/rugby-5th-december-results-and-fixtures/</ref> for sponsorship reasons, is the highest tier of Rugby Union in [[Malta]]. It is sponsored by [[Cisk Lager]] and run by the [[Malta Rugby Football Union]]. Champions of the previous season play the winner of the [[Malta Rugby Union National Cup|Mediterranean Bank Cup]], which runs parallel, in the [[Ray Elliot Cup]], which serves a super cup.
